International Comparisons<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
Data published by Krug et al in 1998 indicated the following rates for gun deaths per 100,000 population:<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
USA                     ?      14.24<br>
<br>
Switzerland           ?        5.31<br>
<br>
Scotland               ?        0.54<br>
<br>
England & Wales  ?        0.41<br>
<br>
Japan                    ?        0.05<br>
<br>
<br>
